Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.96,0:00:09.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa Kasubata sudah mati?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.67,0:00:12.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia bikin aku khawatir.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.26,0:00:15.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu Urusugawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.76,0:00:17.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sini kupeluk.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.89,0:00:20.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kusaba…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.27,0:00:23.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau takkan menemui Kasubata, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.81,0:00:25.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku takkan membiarkanmu pergi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.67,0:02:16.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eru Kusaba.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.09,0:02:19.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Gadis ini…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.34,0:02:22.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia tipe berbahaya yang tak boleh didekati.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.76,0:02:24.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sangat romantis.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.89,0:02:27.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia mudah jatuh cinta\Npada pria di pandangan pertama.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.31,0:02:30.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lewat pencarian dan jalur pribadi,\Ndia selidiki selera mereka mendalam.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.65,0:02:35.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Gadis berbahaya ini\Nmemahami segalanya tentang pria,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.94,0:02:37.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan memerankan "wanita ideal" mereka.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.82,0:02:40.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Korbannya sejauh ini 12 orang.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.37,0:02:45.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aktifkan siber!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.54,0:02:48.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Little Mine Book.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.83,0:02:50.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika menginjak ranjau darat,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.12,0:02:51.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku bisa memakai kemampuan para pria
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.88,0:02:54.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}yang kuambil hingga 120 persen.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.05,0:03:00.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Cepat sekali! Serangannya sangat kuat!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.22,0:03:02.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sticky Love Bomb milikku pun\Ntak bisa menahan kekuatan maskulin ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.76,0:03:03.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Omong-omong,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.97,0:03:07.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}saat cintaku terbalas,\Naku akan langsung kehilangan minat.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.60,0:03:11.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mungkin aku ditakdirkan menjadi wanita\Nyang selamanya mengejar cinta?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.81,0:03:14.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi itulah diriku,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.57,0:03:16.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eru Kusaba.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.23,0:03:19.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau bilang takkan melepaskanku.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.19,0:03:21.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau cuma menghalangi bala bantuan\Nuntuk Kapten.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.74,0:03:24.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Semangat tim seperti itu\Nsama sekali bukan gaya Kelas 1-A.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.03,0:03:26.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau salah paham.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.45,0:03:28.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Wagari sangat kuat.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.41,0:03:30.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kasubata pasti akan segera\Ndikalahkan, bukan?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.62,0:03:31.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saat itu terjadi…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.75,0:03:35.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kasubata, bertahanlah!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.17,0:03:38.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Urusugawa, apa kau yang membalut lukaku?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.22,0:03:44.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika terus begini,\NKasubata bisa jatuh cinta padamu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.89,0:03:47.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku takkan membiarkannya!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.22,0:03:50.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa kau masih romantis\Ndi saat seperti ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.14,0:03:54.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sticky Love Bomb!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.94,0:03:56.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terbanglah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.49,0:04:06.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aduh.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.03,0:04:10.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sial, banyak kekuatan spiritual\Nyang terpakai untuk meredamnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.91,0:04:14.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi dia harusnya terjebak\NSticky Love Bomb dan tak bisa bergerak.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.17,0:04:16.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pakaiannya…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.17,0:04:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tak ada pria di sini,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.08,0:04:21.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}jadi, tak perlu malu, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.22,0:04:24.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lagi pula, di dalam ruangan\Nkita takkan terekam drone siaran langsung.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.30,0:04:25.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ditambah lagi,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.47,0:04:30.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}ini tempat kita harus melepas pakaian, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.90,0:04:36.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tak masalah menunjukkan semua kekuranganmu?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.73,0:04:43.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan menghajarmu\Nlebih keras dari sebelumnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.57,0:04:46.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau takkan punya kesempatan\Nuntuk merayu Kasubata lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.45,0:04:47.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak merayunya!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.08,0:04:50.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa hebatnya dia?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.79,0:04:54.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kasubata…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.00,0:04:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tatapannya menusuk hati.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.08,0:05:00.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia serius dan jantan. Dia sangat keren.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.71,0:05:03.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Enishiro juga keren.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.05,0:05:06.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tak adil kau sekelas dengan mereka.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.05,0:05:08.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Seleramu buruk sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.68,0:05:12.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau selalu berganti pasangan!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.19,0:05:18.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Penampilanmu tak begini saat masuk sekolah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.36,0:05:21.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau mengecat hitam rambutmu\Ndemi menyenangkan Kasubata?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.48,0:05:24.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau tak punya pendirian?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.78,0:05:27.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kusaba, kau punya hobi?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.61,0:05:28.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana denganmu?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.91,0:05:29.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku suka main tenis.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.08,0:05:31.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku juga suka tenis.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.79,0:05:34.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebenarnya aku suka salad teripang.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.66,0:05:37.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Aku terdengar seperti pria tua, kan?\N- Aku suka tunikata.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.33,0:05:40.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau ganti hobimu lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.92,0:05:42.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukankah kau terlalu cepat ganti pacar?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.96,0:05:45.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini bukan sekadar\Nganti latar belakang ponsel.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.09,0:05:48.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini semua bagian dari diriku.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.01,0:05:51.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku serius dengan setiap hubungan!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.14,0:05:54.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku cuma ingin jujur pada perasaanku.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.19,0:06:00.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak mau mendengarnya\Ndari maniak sepertimu!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.90,0:06:05.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tutup mulutmu!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.28,0:06:07.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Rasakan ini!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.36,0:06:10.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Menyerahlah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.66,0:06:12.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Urusugawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.91,0:06:16.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lihat ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.25,0:06:19.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku menyentuhnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.50,0:06:23.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku melakukannya\Ndengan idola favoritmu, Kureha.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.85,0:06:38.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku cuma ingin menakutinya.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.89,0:06:41.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Untung aku membuat foto editan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.56,0:06:44.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia akan trauma secara fisik dan mental.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.57,0:06:47.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia takkan bisa melawan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.36,0:06:50.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Idolamu sama sekali bukan tipeku.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.91,0:06:58.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia sangat arogan\Nhanya karena terlahir kaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.54,0:06:59.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia sangat menyebalkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.54,0:07:01.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia selalu mengamuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.46,0:07:03.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Guru-guru juga pilih kasih padanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.46,0:07:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Meski dunia ini menyebalkan,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.09,0:07:07.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}selama idolaku ada…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.67,0:07:10.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selama dia masih ada di dunia ini,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.13,0:07:13.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}itu sudah cukup bagiku untuk terus maju.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.60,0:07:18.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Suara bas Kureha menusuk tubuhku,\Nmembuatku terbakar semangat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.94,0:07:24.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sticky Love Rope.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.57,0:07:27.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana dia bisa pulih secepat itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.36,0:07:31.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku langsung sadar itu foto editan!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.36,0:07:33.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Meski sempat terkejut,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.62,0:07:36.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku ingat itu foto Instagram-nya\Nsaat sendirian di ranjang rumahnya,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.04,0:07:40.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}pukul 01.18, tanggal 2 Maret tahun lalu!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.91,0:07:41.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.96,0:07:44.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sudah melihat foto itu berkali-kali.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.79,0:07:47.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku membayangkan diriku\Ntidur seranjang dengannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.30,0:07:50.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan remehkan\Npengalamanku mengejar idola!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.17,0:07:53.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Gadis ini sama sepertiku…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.14,0:07:55.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Penggemar sejati!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.72,0:07:57.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selain itu…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.27,0:08:01.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.52,0:08:05.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa ini? Kenapa tiba-tiba…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.94,0:08:07.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ponselku…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.24,0:08:12.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa yang sudah kulakukan?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.78,0:08:14.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nona.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.07,0:08:18.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berbahaya bagi gadis sendirian selarut ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.70,0:08:19.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mau kuantar?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.91,0:08:21.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tutup mulutmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.12,0:08:23.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak mencari Om Senang.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.25,0:08:25.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Om Senang…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.25,0:08:28.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kiyomi Urusugawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.00,0:08:30.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku baru dari rumah sakit.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.76,0:08:32.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.66,0:08:36.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia selalu mengatakan hal menyebalkan,\Njadi, kuharap dia mati saja!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.47,0:08:39.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lalu itu terjadi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.05,0:08:46.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maafkan aku.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.28,0:08:59.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.20,0:09:03.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hanya kita berdua\Nyang bisa melihat kekuatan ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.37,0:09:06.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau membangkitkan bakat luar biasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.34,0:09:10.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Teman sekelasmu baik-baik saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.96,0:09:14.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada banyak orang sepertimu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.38,0:09:16.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Anak-anak yang memiliki siberkinesis.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.55,0:09:18.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Siberkinesis?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.72,0:09:22.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau mau berlatih agar kekuatan ini\Ntak lepas kendali?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.22,0:09:24.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bersama teman-temanmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.56,0:09:26.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukan hanya idolaku, tapi…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.15,0:09:30.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak boleh kalah darimu!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.27,0:09:32.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku juga!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.28,0:09:35.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan meremehkanku!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.61,0:09:37.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku juga bisa bilang begitu padamu!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.37,0:09:42.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika terus begini,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.91,0:09:44.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku yang akan rugi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.62,0:09:48.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sial! Jika terus bertarung,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.04,0:09:50.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku bisa hilang kesadaran!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.75,0:09:52.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aktifkan siber!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.83,0:10:26.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak bisa bergerak lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.71,0:10:29.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.55,0:10:35.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kusaba, kau petarung yang hebat.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.92,0:10:41.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kutarik kembali ucapanku soal kau\Ntak punya harga diri dan hanya berfantasi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.35,0:10:44.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau juga kuat.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.22,0:10:47.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf sudah menyebutmu maniak.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.61,0:10:55.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lagi pula, aku belum pernah\Nmengalami hal seperti itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.90,0:11:01.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Satu kemenangan dan satu seri.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.37,0:11:03.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kelas 1-B sedikit diuntungkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.87,0:11:07.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini sangat berbeda dari\NPertarungan Antarkelas sebelumnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.16,0:11:09.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kelas 1-A, dipimpin oleh Wagari, mungkin…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.00,0:11:14.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pak Azaki, jangan terlalu cepat\Nterbawa suasana.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.42,0:11:16.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pak Nanzo,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.26,0:11:18.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}pertandingan ini bukan antara kita berdua.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.84,0:11:20.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Menyedihkan sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.09,0:11:24.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nanzo, dulu kau sangat menghormatiku.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.35,0:11:26.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kepala Sekolah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.64,0:11:30.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Reaksi akun gaib terdeteksi\Ndi Virtual Kusatsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.27,0:11:32.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Akun gaib muncul?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.23,0:11:35.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pembacaannya samar, tapi akurat.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.44,0:11:36.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pak Azaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.73,0:11:39.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini bukan salah satu leluconmu, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.36,0:11:40.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tentu saja bukan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.15,0:11:43.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tolong perintahkan penyelidikan.\NKepala Sekolah,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.74,0:11:46.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hubungi staf di lokasi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.08,0:11:48.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.29,0:11:51.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sepertinya,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.00,0:11:55.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}bukan Nanzo atau akademi yang mengatur ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.13,0:11:57.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa yang terjadi?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.09,0:12:01.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sial, aku tak bisa melakukan apa pun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.38,0:12:04.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tubuhku terus gemetar.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.85,0:12:09.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku payah sekali. Sangat memalukan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.31,0:12:12.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa yang terjadi?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.15,0:12:19.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak bisa menyerangnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.53,0:12:23.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apiku bahkan tak bisa\Nmenyentuh ujung pakaiannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.20,0:12:27.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pria ini…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.41,0:12:31.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa yang dia lalui hanya dalam dua pekan?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.33,0:12:35.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pak Azaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.71,0:12:38.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada yang ingin kutanyakan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.88,0:12:43.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.34,0:12:46.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pak Azaki, tolong beri tahu aku.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.68,0:12:49.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa ada cara mengaktifkan\Nsiber tanpa ponsel?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.64,0:12:52.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tak ada cara seperti itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.23,0:12:53.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana bisa?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.39,0:12:55.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi anak itu, Surugi,\Ntak menggunakan ponsel!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.02,0:12:58.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitu rupanya. Itu maksudmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.69,0:13:01.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Perkembangannya agak cepat.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.94,0:13:05.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi dalam kondisimu saat ini,\Nkau mungkin mencapai tahap berikutnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.11,0:13:08.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tahap berikutnya?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.03,0:13:09.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dengar.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.95,0:13:14.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mengaktifkan siber langsung dari ponsel\Nadalah metode standar.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.21,0:13:15.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namun,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.87,0:13:18.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}alih-alih mengeluarkan\Nkekuatan spiritual melalui ponsel,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.34,0:13:20.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kau menariknya kembali ke tubuhmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.92,0:13:22.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Menariknya kembali ke tubuhku?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.84,0:13:25.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lalu melepaskannya dari titik lain.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.06,0:13:35.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Rasakan aliran kekuatan spiritual\Ndi perutmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.44,0:13:38.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak bisa melakukannya…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.31,0:13:40.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Setelah menguasainya,\Nbahkan tanpa memegang ponsel,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.69,0:13:43.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}selama ponsel menyentuh tubuhmu,\Nkau bisa mengaktifkan siber.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.82,0:13:46.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kobaran Api Hantu-mu
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.95,0:13:53.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}bisa membara lebih bebas.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.41,0:13:57.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku minta mekanik\Nmemasang penahan di ponselku.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.75,0:14:00.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kekuatan spiritual mengalir\Ndi tubuhku sekarang.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.59,0:14:02.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.92,0:14:04.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lawan aku.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.59,0:14:08.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Enflame, Mata.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.05,0:14:11.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih, Pak Azaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.10,0:14:15.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selama tanganku bebas,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.98,0:14:18.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku bisa membuat teknik bertarungku\Nlebih beragam.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.40,0:14:19.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aori.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.69,0:14:22.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih, Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.20,0:14:28.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa aku tak bisa menyerangnya?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.57,0:14:31.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sama sekali tak bisa menggapainya.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.49,0:14:33.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.29,0:14:38.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Serang aku. Serang aku lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.00,0:14:41.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terus serang, Enishiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.92,0:14:44.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lagi. Belum cukup.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.46,0:14:48.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Masih belum cukup…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.63,0:14:52.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Enishiro, ini belum cukup!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.14,0:14:56.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini kesempatanku!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.89,0:15:01.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kena kau!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.10,0:15:03.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Daging hangus memang yang terbaik!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.69,0:15:05.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Biar kudengar teriakanmu!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.32,0:15:06.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Enflame, Bahu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.69,0:15:07.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Enflame, Bahu!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.61,0:15:08.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kebal Api!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.03,0:15:10.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.03,0:15:13.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Api seperti ini takkan bisa membakarku.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.67,0:15:22.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana? Kau mau menyerah?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.75,0:15:24.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.88,0:15:30.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sama sekali tak memuaskan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.64,0:15:34.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau hanya menjadi lebih kuat.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.60,0:15:41.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau hanya membawa rasa sakit.\NSama sekali tak menyenangkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.65,0:15:45.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tak ada kebencian terhadapku\Ndalam seranganmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.32,0:15:49.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Suka dan benci itu sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.70,0:15:54.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu emosi yang sama kuatnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.16,0:15:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Di balik telepon,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.29,0:15:58.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}ada banyak orang
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.04,0:16:00.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}yang membenciku.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.83,0:16:02.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sayang sekali
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.25,0:16:03.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku tak bisa melihat wajah mereka.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.17,0:16:10.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini belum cukup…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.92,0:16:12.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini buruk.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.26,0:16:14.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lagi…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.89,0:16:17.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benci aku lebih lagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.85,0:16:20.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dasar bedebah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.10,0:16:25.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak percaya harus sekelas denganmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.31,0:16:29.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Rasa keadilanku sekuat tenaga melawanmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.74,0:16:32.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi sebenarnya itu lebih baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.16,0:16:35.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}daripada keadilan setengah hati.\NItu jauh lebih baik
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.20,0:16:37.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebenarnya, aku suka itu darimu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.08,0:16:44.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia membenci sekaligus menyukaiku.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.54,0:16:46.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pengalaman yang belum pernah kurasakan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.63,0:16:49.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kesenangan yang belum pernah kurasakan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.17,0:16:53.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Enishiro, kau membenciku, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.84,0:16:56.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ingat saat aku membakar sesuatu\Nyang berharga bagimu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.72,0:17:01.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lampiaskan kemarahan dan kesedihanmu\Nkepadaku seperti sebelumnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.31,0:17:03.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bawa aku ke puncak!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.15,0:17:08.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak peduli denganmu, Keroco.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.60,0:17:11.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia tak peduli!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.35,0:17:14.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mari kita selesaikan pertarungan ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.85,0:17:17.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Enflame, Kaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.70,0:17:19.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini lompatan super yang ditingkatkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.07,0:17:23.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jaraknya sekitar 50 meter.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.71,0:17:28.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yang kurang darimu, Aori,\Nadalah jurus istimewamu sendiri.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.21,0:17:34.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tendangan yang diperkuat\Ndan kecepatan jatuh karena gravitasi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.26,0:17:35.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Teknik Kobaran Api Hantu!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.88,0:17:38.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Api Langit!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.44,0:17:50.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pria ini…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.94,0:17:54.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia tahu dia bukan tandinganku.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.24,0:17:56.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa dia menyerang langsung?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.86,0:17:58.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kukuru!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.07,0:18:00.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ren!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.45,0:18:02.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku datang membantumu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.41,0:18:05.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sekarang dua lawan satu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.01,0:18:19.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kukuru, kau harus selamat.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.85,0:18:26.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tak ada info soal murid Kelas 1-A itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.94,0:18:31.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya, hanya dia yang tak ikut\Ndalam pertarungan sebelumnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.86,0:18:34.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia tak bermain agar jumlah kita sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.32,0:18:36.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kiri Namekawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.20,0:18:38.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika bertemu dengannya, jangan lengah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.36,0:18:40.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tak ada yang tahu kemampuannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.28,0:18:41.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Wah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.49,0:18:44.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aktifkan siber!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.41,0:18:46.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aplikasi Hipnosis!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.38,0:18:52.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Izinkan aku memperkenalkan diri.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.96,0:18:54.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku Kiri Namekawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.13,0:18:59.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hobiku mengamati serangga\Ndan membuat berita palsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.80,0:19:06.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Senang melihat orang kurang informasi\Ntertipu oleh kebohongan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.31,0:19:08.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini seperti mengamati serangga.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.02,0:19:11.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Siberkinesisku adalah Aplikasi Hipnosis.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.44,0:19:13.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selama aku membuat lawan menatap layar,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.77,0:19:17.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku bisa membuat mereka menuruti perintahku.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.57,0:19:18.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Perintah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.99,0:19:22.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Serang Kukuru Kasubata.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.41,0:19:32.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku menyerang Kukuru.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.17,0:19:39.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kukuru…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.76,0:19:44.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mereka berdua kehilangan kemampuan\Nbertarung di saat bersamaan, Wagari.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.93,0:19:46.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sudah kuduga itu perbuatanmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.56,0:19:50.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Akhir yang menjijikkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.14,0:19:53.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sungguh tak menyukaimu, Namekawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.65,0:19:57.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi aku sangat menyukaimu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.40,0:20:02.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baumu seperti lem yang kupakai di TK.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.45,0:20:05.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah, sekarang saatnya\Nmenyelesaikan pertarungan ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.74,0:20:08.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Temukan dalang pengecut\Nyang bersembunyi itu…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.50,0:20:13.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini belum berakhir, Wagari.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.83,0:20:15.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.51,0:20:21.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku mulai sedikit marah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.68,0:20:23.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Biar aku mengendalikanmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.05,0:20:25.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan lihat layarnya, Kukuru!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.76,0:20:27.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan lihat!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.43,0:20:30.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Perintah, Menari Liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.23,0:20:32.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Menarilah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.65,0:20:37.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lepaskan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.62,0:20:49.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kemampuan psikis yang tak sempurna\Nbisa jadi bumerang bagi penggunanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.33,0:20:52.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia menggunakan raungan\Nuntuk memanfaatkan celah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.08,0:20:56.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia memanfaatkan ketidakstabilan\Nuntuk mengganggu kekuatan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.25,0:21:01.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bahkan sekarang,\Ndia masih bisa meraung keras.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.34,0:21:04.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tampaknya keadilan yang menyimpang pun\Nmemiliki keyakinan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.22,0:21:05.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika aku tak bisa memotong tekadmu,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.76,0:21:07.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kali ini, aku akan "memotongnya".
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.89,0:21:10.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan melumpuhkanmu secara fisik.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.81,0:21:14.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau tak bisa kabur lewat jendela lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.15,0:21:16.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kukuru, kau akan mati!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.40,0:21:17.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Menyerahlah!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.07,0:21:19.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pak Azaki, kau juga lihat, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.03,0:21:21.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Umumkan "kehilangan kemampuan bertarung"!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.90,0:21:22.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Azaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.07,0:21:24.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pak Azaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.24,0:21:26.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau mencoba membunuh muridmu?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.24,0:21:27.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Azaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.16,0:21:28.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pak Azaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.49,0:21:29.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Diam!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.16,0:21:32.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalian semua, diam!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.25,0:21:34.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika aku menyerah sekarang,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.08,0:21:35.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}itu juga akan jadi akhir bagiku.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.84,0:21:41.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kukuru, kenapa nekat sejauh ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.55,0:21:43.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.09,0:21:45.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kali terakhir, kupikir kalah itu wajar.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.51,0:21:48.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku cuma bisa\Nmengaktifkan siber sekali lagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.76,0:21:51.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aktifkan siber!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.94,0:21:56.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kukuru.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.19,0:22:02.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu…
